@startuml SeqD_D07_Emergency_Patient_Search

title SeqD_D07 — Search Patient by ID or Name (Emergency Access)

actor "Doctor" as DOC
participant "Global Search UI" as UI
participant "DoctorController" as CTRL
participant "DoctorService" as SVC
participant "AppDbContext" as DB
participant "NotificationService" as NOTIF

== Search ==

DOC -> UI : Type patient name or Patient ID\nin global search bar
UI -> CTRL : GET /api/doctor/patients/search?query=...
CTRL -> SVC : SearchAllPatientsAsync(query)
SVC -> DB : SELECT patients WHERE name LIKE query\nOR patient_id = query\n(ALL records, not restricted to assigned list)
DB --> SVC : results

alt No patient found
  SVC --> CTRL : empty list
  CTRL --> UI : 200 OK — empty
  UI --> DOC : "No matching patient record found"\nSuggest verifying ID with Administrator
end

SVC --> CTRL : patient list
CTRL --> UI : 200 OK — results
UI --> DOC : Display results:\nname, Patient ID, DOB (partially masked),\nassigned doctor name

== Emergency Access Modal ==

DOC -> UI : Select target patient
UI --> DOC : Show mandatory "Emergency Access" modal:\n"You are about to access a patient not assigned to you.\nThis access will be logged and the assigned doctor notified.\nPlease state your clinical reason."

DOC -> UI : Enter clinical reason + confirm

alt Doctor cancels without submitting
  UI -> CTRL : POST /api/doctor/patients/{patientId}/emergency-access/declined
  CTRL -> SVC : LogAccessAttemptAsync(patientId, doctorId, Declined)
  SVC -> DB : INSERT AuditLog (status = Declined by User)
  DB --> SVC : logged
  CTRL --> UI : 403 Forbidden
  UI --> DOC : Access blocked
end

alt Reason fewer than 10 characters
  UI --> DOC : Reject — highlight minimum character requirement
end

UI -> CTRL : POST /api/doctor/patients/{patientId}/emergency-access\n{reason}
CTRL -> SVC : GrantEmergencyAccessAsync(patientId, doctorId, reason)

SVC -> DB : INSERT EmergencyAccessLog\n(requestingDoctorId, patientId,\ntimestamp, reason) — immutable
SVC -> DB : SELECT full patient medical record (read-only)
DB --> SVC : patient profile
SVC -> NOTIF : NotifyAssignedDoctorAsync(patientId, requestingDoctorId)
NOTIF --> SVC : assigned doctor notified

SVC --> CTRL : read-only patient profile
CTRL --> UI : 200 OK — patient record (read-only session)
UI --> DOC : Display patient full record\n(read-only — no add/edit/test request actions available)

== Alternative: Session ends ==

alt Session ends or doctor logs out
  SVC -> DB : Revoke emergency access token
  DB --> SVC : access revoked
end

@enduml
